                  </persName>
             sworn. - I am a constable, (produces the saw); I received it at the sign of the Bell, from Pearce.(The saw was identified by Pearce).</p>
               <p>Prisoner's defence. As the gentleman swears so hard, I leave myself to the mercy of the Court.</p>
               <p>One witness was called, who gave him a good character.</p>
